craterdog.core

Class Composite<C extends Composite<C>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • craterdog.core.Composite<C>
  • Type Parameters:
    C - The concrete type of the composite object.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Cloneable, Comparable<C>

    public abstract class Composite<C extends Composite<C>>
extends Object
implements Cloneable, Comparable<C>
    This abstract class provides implementations for the standard methods defined in the Object class that can be used by all composite objects. Since the java.lang.Cloneable interface is essentially broken it has been disabled and replace with a suitable copy() method.
    Author:
    Derk Norton
